desc: FernSanJuan a store in Friday Harbor, Washington. Shop for Art, Paintings, Greeting Cards, Clothing, Scarves, Paintings and Home Decor and Specialty Items.

layout.text: Hello! I'm so glad you're here!
Welcome to the online shop for my brick and mortar store, FERN, on beautiful San Juan Island in the Salish Sea. The place to find all things pretty, calming, colorful, and fun.
